{"h6cefb483gda38g4467g9c0ag1754834fec81": ["*Grunt.*", "0f8ef61e-cb63-49e1-a242-677173bff5e0", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_General_GruntingKid.html", "c93c5381-4b99-3a3f-e261-6df595a8a8c5"], "h99bd57fagfe0bg4f1cg962eg2a8d72166eac": ["*He stares right past you as if you're invisible. Or boring.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_General_GruntingKid.html", "7cf615fb-1b0e-c686-b1ca-196342b19bcb"], "h3b25b560g0e64g4b93g8f5dg20559fe215a2": ["Are you all right?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_General_GruntingKid.html", "3a33bf81-572d-1480-f5fd-8aa881e743a7"], "h153f1800g6f07g412fg8cb8g80e04568d81e": ["*Grunt.*", "0f8ef61e-cb63-49e1-a242-677173bff5e0", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_General_GruntingKid.html", "af628df8-8a7e-8940-fc56-d53084e4185e"], "hc47441f2g8b7cg4f0fg91b9gbcccf5675851": ["I see. Anything else on your mind?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_General_GruntingKid.html", "e75d6f7a-a108-f7f7-87c3-72e0141b2b69"], "h99378ddfgce38g4e15ga5d1ga9d12ad0fda3": ["*Grunt!*", "0f8ef61e-cb63-49e1-a242-677173bff5e0", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_General_GruntingKid.html", "0f6e73ff-d1b2-07a6-32b4-224f9ed0f59d"], "h724be48cg96ddg4a9ag99deg812eaac3bc01": ["*He's still staring right past you.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_General_GruntingKid.html", "5ba3b2ba-f311-acde-e243-6580f1265f1a"], "h03956b26g5a42g411cg8041g5b0cfc04581a": ["<i>Grunt.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_General_GruntingKid.html", "60a076f6-fee0-58fe-467e-01157f78ffdd"], "hd2ea6458gdec9g4897ga9e2g433ee9429342": ["*Grunt.*", "0f8ef61e-cb63-49e1-a242-677173bff5e0", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_General_GruntingKid.html", "4c7832f2-c6de-b1ed-8bdf-369544b378c0"], "hdcf5090dg408cg466bgb7bbgab403dc8b6bf": ["<i>Turn around to see what has his attention.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_General_GruntingKid.html", "bbd45492-66fb-5cec-ebf7-a8a9fccfd2ff"], "h4054b950g07ddg4922g961egbd71e3aa102f": ["*You see nothing out of the ordinary.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_General_GruntingKid.html", "bad87002-c5fb-e8ec-054c-7778d193ce43"], "h4157d157g7a9eg4cbfg8796gbf84bd0b130f": ["<i>As you turn back, the child slips between the rocks.</i>", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_General_GruntingKid.html", "f23bdccc-c1a4-a728-9f7b-d880edc792e0"], "h7cca0f22g62e9g40c8g9f1dga287b8caa707": ["<i>Search the rocks for an opening.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_General_GruntingKid.html", "da0ec023-0464-1916-d0fd-d62ea80277cb"], "hea6ec6eegaa03g44b4g9949ga43c28d03ca9": ["*You find the edges of a concealed entrance.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_General_GruntingKid.html", "2c3bdda0-c3e8-417f-07a4-e6bfbdfa2d33"], "h83eee634gda97g422bgb711g2a08b70f0d32": ["*No trigger or handle, though. No way to open it.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_General_GruntingKid.html", "1e617371-0af9-7c48-82fe-368c3438ade0"], "h28d8e5d2gc29dg4b4ag98edgd9a74a6837fc": ["*You look the rocks over, but find no sign of a way through.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_General_GruntingKid.html", "8112709e-d4c5-039d-7d3b-427459afd185"], "h1d668735gba22g4950g864dg116f39fc4019": ["<i>Examine the rocks for anything out of the ordinary.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_General_GruntingKid.html", "ca6e0a84-48e1-77e7-3117-a3fdf5a11a6f"], "hb8ee8d31gdab5g4168g9537g4670adf660d6": ["<i>Study the rocks for a secret passage.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_General_GruntingKid.html", "3ab58cc8-dcd0-b2b4-6480-6ba6b09fe5a1"], "hca6e154fgcb2eg48cbg9f93g9845dfa224c2": ["<i>Leave.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_General_GruntingKid.html", "af5481c6-dea8-b544-c2d8-42c4491ff30b"], "hca7e6359g5b4fg405fg9f83gd0bcdefaf1a3": ["*When you turn back, there's no trace of the child.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_General_GruntingKid.html", "46bd2bb0-38a3-1a23-f5df-c641afc74dca"], "h1b53933cgffaeg4f9bg83b8ga43e81d978b3": ["Hello? ", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_General_GruntingKid.html", "6c1822d6-90a0-1908-bebf-84e794c84a12"], "h98789c4agd1b8g4d94g98cfg76a55213c094": ["Doni, isn't it? I want to see the Dragon's Lair.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_General_GruntingKid.html", "c08a1fdf-48e5-2753-82aa-f0dfb2804080"], "h6a3949d0gfe85g4138gbcaeg9ba1ff51fd7d": ["<i>Turn around to see what he's looking at.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_General_GruntingKid.html", "d60bb0a0-9a1c-9602-686a-8bfba56e4b09"], "haefdaa0bg5e40g44ecg8e88g48cc62b2805f": ["<i>Leave.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_General_GruntingKid.html", "513b279f-cb96-246f-1131-8c577854917e"], "hf14d361egf449g481dgab80gaca96b79131f": ["*Grunt.*", "0f8ef61e-cb63-49e1-a242-677173bff5e0", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_General_GruntingKid.html", "a5ab7395-fd8a-1195-908b-803f8d9fd752"], "h616cce1bg403dg41c6g910fg5830fdb064df": ["*He stares past you, as if you aren't there at all.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_General_GruntingKid.html", "8fbefefb-f594-e5df-afcc-eaff296fcd82"], "ha82e70a5g7becg4f35g8fd8ge8b4b7bd364b": ["Hey. Thanks for showing me the door.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_General_GruntingKid.html", "50b6b833-7b32-cfd7-9710-77a51482691e"], "h9b258492gfaccg4862g83bbgb0f9151ecdcc": ["*Grunt.*", "0f8ef61e-cb63-49e1-a242-677173bff5e0", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_General_GruntingKid.html", "c85ccbf8-0421-68d0-0682-420de75cae5d"], "hf7e31745gd0e0g43b5gaaaag07ddc5162d0f": ["Hello?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_General_GruntingKid.html", "0593a6b7-968d-05bd-fd11-441d937821c8"], "hf000ac31gf655g4fafg80eegcc391cd4463a": ["*Grunt!*", "0f8ef61e-cb63-49e1-a242-677173bff5e0", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_General_GruntingKid.html", "18467d88-3811-1189-c5f5-1ac77f854e49"], "h03c85187g7f21g43a2gac03g06554642dffc": ["*His eyes flicker to yours for an instant, then away, as if it hurts to look at you.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_General_GruntingKid.html", "f749811e-d273-9778-524e-9a7a4f5e924c"], "ha944bcaeg70d3g4e15ga4bcg9153e0eb4d23": ["Where the hells did you disappear to before?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_General_GruntingKid.html", "77788521-d422-809e-7df9-194dfe59a69e"], "had770c81gabdbg441cgb4fbg5bcef742098f": ["*Grunt.*", "0f8ef61e-cb63-49e1-a242-677173bff5e0", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_General_GruntingKid.html", "d44db5b5-f182-57bf-e80a-6a2a86ab2524"], "ha2cf924eg0cf9g4727g9c98gcf6efb6f9b09": ["*Watching his hands, you realise he's miming opening something.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_General_GruntingKid.html", "4b516aee-4c73-3c21-3023-38410977ce88"], "h8471f307g45fbg49cagb2aeg5d5fa7ad2be8": ["<i>Read his mind.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_General_GruntingKid.html", "065ecf93-a7be-aeee-01d8-d511ba3efcfa"], "h1310113cgd1f8g460cg9280g14d160830526": ["<i>Got to keep watch... but it's so bright and noisy here. Want to be back in the hideout.</i>", "0f8ef61e-cb63-49e1-a242-677173bff5e0", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_General_GruntingKid.html", "f87e7011-d1a6-c2e9-da4c-783a9c031d40"], "h66e67077g9ce7g4aa0g8ecbged64b82fa842": ["It's bright and noisy up here, huh? I wish there were somewhere darker to rest.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_General_GruntingKid.html", "7722534a-bc14-ba23-6c42-e8771ccad884"], "hf33bd40fg6219g468cg9a2bg62ed3e02ddef": ["*He nods, then reaches for a concealed hatch.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_General_GruntingKid.html", "1ca79eca-87be-1681-7935-99b9a2495bde"], "hb9e36baegc99eg4fdaga2fdgd088cc1db054": ["Is it a chest? A door? Can you show me where it is?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_General_GruntingKid.html", "b6ae1d2c-6ef7-e811-fcb8-0a8a7f81dcc6"], "hc8f308d8g14efg490agbbc6g9a9710205bed": ["*Grunt.*", "0f8ef61e-cb63-49e1-a242-677173bff5e0", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_General_GruntingKid.html", "7a45ff35-b6f1-8fe7-c957-aee67a12bb16"], "h651c6413gf5b8g43afgaf3dg9bd0d8090e92": ["<i>Leave.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_General_GruntingKid.html", "072b2fb5-1045-85dc-d18b-9f4a7a284068"], "hf2bac745gd080g47cdga6a9g490a01a23bbf": ["*Grunt.*", "0f8ef61e-cb63-49e1-a242-677173bff5e0", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_General_GruntingKid.html", "466a1ad2-6909-3d90-f84c-bbfde14344da"], "h06a98a56gb77fg4908ga7fdg6880ac85d67f": ["<i>Leave.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_General_GruntingKid.html", "3d8cee58-59f1-cb46-0bdd-1c3d7ad8fcb4"], "h3fa8bed8gf77ag4a57g86d1g3190c9c43de0": ["*He's trying to tell you something, but you can't make any sense of it.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_General_GruntingKid.html", "977a6bfe-beaa-6c18-3da5-531e99c23c37"], "h95705937g5975g46d0ga3d5gff0e8f1f0dd2": ["Maybe some gold would catch your attention? ([GEN_CheckMagicPocketGold_6057ad05-9492-4630-9f0a-be548b134c54])", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_General_GruntingKid.html", "7a95bf56-7fb4-6020-0013-96c78daeb20a"], "haf61b5d2g8b3ag4e0eg8fdbgb43f5f1f3921": ["*Grunt.*", "0f8ef61e-cb63-49e1-a242-677173bff5e0", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_General_GruntingKid.html", "caf2dcf4-d096-6837-a85c-f18782d5dc38"], "hfdc72661g4758g4858ga43bgbf64004f6c8a": ["<i>Turn to see what he's looking at.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_General_GruntingKid.html", "bb05e9d9-4d33-5f84-954b-eb2a9d2993d0"], "ha41bc08cgb757g485cg97f4g587e33d37635": ["*He's gone. Again.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_General_GruntingKid.html", "a3eaa028-b15c-9231-1eb5-3945b40cd249"], "hb09bdd8eg691bg425bg9d15gdf1db6088964": ["<i>Leave.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_General_GruntingKid.html", "9594f71d-e0e0-efd5-0510-c8444a41851a"], "h7677c748gf79ag489eg82dag4cc242214267": ["*Grunt.*", "0f8ef61e-cb63-49e1-a242-677173bff5e0", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_General_GruntingKid.html", "ebf59d38-01de-616c-a07b-1689f1dc5fd5"]}